import React, {useState} from "react";
import {
	Row,
	Col,
	Card,
	CardBody,
	CardTitle,
	Container,
	Modal,
	ModalHeader,
	ModalBody,
	ModalFooter,
	CardImg,
	Button,
	CustomInput,
	CardText,
	Form,
	FormGroup,
	Label,
	Input,
	FormText,
} from "reactstrap";

const AddUser = (props) => {
	const [modal, setModal] = useState(false);

	const toggle = () => setModal(!modal);
	return (
		<React.Fragment>
			<Modal isOpen={modal} centered={true} toggle={toggle}>
				<ModalHeader toggle={toggle}>AÃ±adir usuarios</ModalHeader>
				<ModalBody>
					<Form>
						<FormGroup>
							<Label for="fullname">Nombre completo</Label>
							<Input
								type="text"
								name="text"
								id="fullname"
								placeholder="E.g: John Doe"
							/>
						</FormGroup>
						<FormGroup>
							<Label for="age">Edad</Label>
							<Input type="text" name="age" id="age" />
						</FormGroup>
						<Label for="gender">Sexo</Label>
						<FormGroup check>
							<Label check>
								<Input type="radio" name="gender" defaultChecked /> Masculino
							</Label>
						</FormGroup>
						<FormGroup check>
							<Label check>
								<Input type="radio" name="gender" /> Femenino
							</Label>
						</FormGroup>
						<FormGroup className="mt-3">
							<FormGroup>
								<Label for="exampleFile">Foto del rostro</Label>
								<Input type="file" name="file" id="exampleFile" className="" />
								<FormText color="muted">
									Formatos permitidos: .jpg y .png
								</FormText>
							</FormGroup>
						</FormGroup>
					</Form>
				</ModalBody>
				<ModalFooter>
					<Button color="primary" onClick={toggle}>
						Guardar
					</Button>{" "}
					<Button color="secondary" onClick={toggle}>
						Cancelar
					</Button>
				</ModalFooter>
			</Modal>
		</React.Fragment>
	);
};

export default AddUser;
